<ep:title>Welcome to <ep:phrase ref="archive_name" /></ep:title>
<ep:body>

<p>Welcome to this generic eprint server, running the default configuration for <a href="http://software.eprints.org/">GNU EPrints repository software</a>.</p>

<p><a href="information.html">More information</a> is available about the repository.</p>

<ep:phrase ref="ruler" /> 
<div align="center">
<form method="get" accept-charset="utf-8" action="{$config{perl_url}}/search">
